Kobalt is Lowe's house tool brand — built for durability and precision. This 100-piece set delivers the essentials every workshop needs, from sockets and drivers to wrenches and bits.

Your $100 MyLowes Card works across tools, appliances, décor, and any home improvement project. MyLowe's Rewards keeps delivering member perks and savings all year long.

Kobalt 100-Piece Tool Set

$100 MyLowes Card

Redeem Your $100 Card + Kobalt Tool Set

Ref: 1234-5678-9012-3456

I think the easiest way to handle it is to just pick a day and go for it.

We can adjust the timing later if something comes up.

I've been meaning to ask you about that project you mentioned a while ago.

Did you ever get around to trying it out?

I remember you said it sounded interesting but you weren't sure where to start.

Sometimes the hardest part is just taking the first step.

Once you begin, everything else starts to fall into place and it feels less overwhelming.

I had a similar experience with something I was putting off for weeks.

Finally sat down and did it, and it only took about an hour.

I kept thinking it would be a huge effort but it was actually pretty straightforward.

Let me know if you want to compare notes or just chat about it sometime.

I'm always happy to listen and offer a different perspective if that helps.

We all need a second opinion now and then.

